Hello everyone, my name is Paul Head, I’m a Casting Director and producer in Los Angeles ***(you can learn more about me here → ***www.pauldhead.com and https://bodegapictures.com/paul-head. ***I’m working on a new documentary series for a major cable network about people whose husband or wife has suddenly gone missing or abandoned them.*** I’m curious if you know anyone in your community whose husband or wife has suddenly left, run away, or disappeared — and their spouse is still searching for them? *People who are chosen for the show are compensated and will receive expert help.*

**Email:** casting@bodegapictures.com

**Application: **https://abandonedspouseshortapp.castingcrane.com/

Hey guys, I'm running a taster session for the screen acting class this Friday for only a fiver! 

In the session, you'll get to practice on a given scene over a couple of takes and I'll also go through the three programs of this autumn: 
* Screen acting drop-in 
* Screen acting Monthly workshop (over 4weeks) to develop presence and get confident on camera. 
* The directing actors Workshop with the last monday of each month with actors in the room! 
* More info at interactors.co.uk @ : info.interactors@gmail.com Make sure you book the ticket for friday via the website if you wish to come! Looking forward to seeing you there!  whttps://www.instagram.com/p/DOeaxfCDLI_/?igsh=MWU0ZHg5aGh5cmI0OQ==

topComments.text: Hello, I was just wondering where abouts this taster will take place and what company is this with?

items.text:
Amazing opportunity for business owners!

Get paid to take part in a super fun, fast-paced game show for a major YouTube channel.

We’re looking for bold, brilliant entrepreneurs — from fresh startups to multi-million-pound empires — who have big personalities and love being on camera. If you’re the kind of business owner who lights up a room, we want you!

This is a chance to promote your business, have a laugh, and get paid doing it.

Please note we are looking for people who are in or near London or are happy to travel themselves there.

💥 Tag a business owner who’d smash this opportunity
📧 Or apply now: casper@casperblackcasting.com

attachments.ocrText: May be an image of 5 people and text that says 'CASTING CALL: BUSINESS OWNERS ? Calling bold, brilliant entrepreneurs we're casting for a fun, fast-paced game show for a major client's Youtube channel. PAID OPPORTUNITY West London 2-3 hour shoot early October YouTube game show Don't miss the chance to promote your business! Email: casper@casperblackcasting.com'

Vi lover et kreativt fællesskab, masser af nye kontakter og oplevelser, du kan bruge i dit CV eller studie.

Vi glæder os til at høre fra dig – og vi har brug for dig NU! 💡

items.text:
Hi everyone . I’ve not posted in groups in a long time . I took a break from acting full time almost six years ago when I nearly lost my little girl nine times in one year  to an illness. 
I spent those six years, training , making connections and friends. Some directors, producers and writers from the likes of Netflix , Warner Bros, Lionsgate etc and some known actors . I wrote scripts that have now been sold to Lionsgate directors and being read by Pierce Brosnan, Samuel L Jackson and many more . 
I changed my whole outlook on acting and the industry and Instead for the last six years it’s been my only goal to help as many actors as I possibly can . I’ve self funded features to help get as many actors and crew seen as I can , always circulating new actors and new crew every film. 
I spent the last six years building an acting curriculum and opened The Foundry Acting Studio after I not only exceeded spotlight approval by over three times but the studio is also SAG recognised too and soon to be other organisations. 
I’ve had actors come to my class for three or four weeks and leave other major schools they were training at for three to four years. 

I offer in person. Online and one to ones. Which all information can be found on the page or by messaging The Foundry Page. 

I get it trust me . New acting classes , new showreel offers , new headshot specialists . There’s always doubt and to be honest what I’ve noticed a lot recently in groups is a lot of hate , a lot of abuse and I’ve seen people being attacked left , right and centre in this industry for posting a headshot or looking work. This industry is an absolutely amazing place , if we all pick each other up. So please keep your hate to yourself . All you’re doing is commenting and people are never going to work with you if you’re rude , foul mouthed or ignorant . 

So yes I understand people being weary of new things but I’m hoping we’ve answered a lot below and again. Like the biggest schools out there.  I am spotlight approved , but I’m also the only independent studio in the U.K. to be SAG recognised and soon to be more . This proves legitimacy. 

So if you’re an actor or starting acting and you want real training , check out the post below. Also if you’re a good person , support other actors and pick people up rather than putting people down. Then you’ll fit perfectly. 

Again . Help each other . Pick each other up. Support each other and be kind to each other . Show new actors that the industry can be a wonderful place . 

Also …. We are the only acting studio making full industry professional feature films and we cast from our students. 

So message us now ….. hope to meet a lot of you soon and keep being fantastic and pushing for that dream

sharedPost.text:
🎬 The Foundry Acting Studio 🎬

Train. Work. Belong.

Where world-class coaching meets real screen credits.

At The Foundry, we don’t do hype, we do results. 

📚Our coach is an internationally trained actor who paused his own career for five years to build a rigorous, modern curriculum from the ground up. (For the record: the world’s best acting coaches aren’t always front-of-camera stars, coaching and acting are different crafts. Ours happens to do both, and he’s now stepping back on set while leading this programme.)

✅️Verified. Recognised. Trusted.
 • Spotlight-approved training (and then some). When Spotlight reviewed our curriculum, it exceeded their requirements by roughly three times.
 • SAG-recognised. We’re one of very few independent UK studios to be both Spotlight-approved and SAG-recognised, with more professional bodies in progress.
 • Our curriculum has been reviewed by established actors, directors, producers and casting directors. Their feedback is consistent: “This is the calibre you’d expect from a major, prestigious franchise school.”

✅️Training that turns into work
 • We own our kit: RED cinema cameras, top-tier lenses, pro-grade sound, the works. No hired “showreel days.”
 • We produce our own professional features and shorts and cast from our students.
 • Speaking roles guaranteed in our in-house features/shorts for committed students who complete the pathway, because the goal isn’t just growth; it’s getting you working.

✅️Accessible. Supportive. Serious.
 • £100 every four weeks for in-person classes or online classes.
 • We also offer one-to-one's intensives to go deeper, faster.
 • We welcome beginners, returners and working actors, and all different backgrounds. Whether you’re on a pension, benefits, full-time or part-time work, we’ve designed this to be accessible and judgment-free. No nepotism. No gatekeeping. Just craft.

🎥Why actors choose The Foundry Acting Studio 
 • Curriculum: far beyond the minimum, Spotlight-approved ×3.
 • Pathways: SAG-recognised, with additional organisations pending.
 • Industry connection: active relationships with professionals who’ve worked across Netflix, Warner Bros., Lionsgate, FX, HBO, and more.
 • Outcomes: high-level training plus on-set experience and speaking roles in our productions.

📢What actors are saying
 • “Four weeks here taught me more than two years at one of the North’s biggest schools.”
 • “After one 1-to-1 session, I left the class I’d attended for 18 months, the difference was night and day.”
 • “I moved from another ‘top’ school after four weeks at The Foundry, no comparison.”

📚What you get with us📚
 • High-level curriculum which has taken five years to perfect.
 • Spotlight-approved curriculum, SAG-recognised pathways.
 • Guaranteed speaking roles in our in-house shorts/features (for students who complete the pathway).
 • Professional sets with RED cameras, cinema lenses, and pro sound.
 • £100/4 weeks, in-person + online, with optional one-day intensives.
 • A community that’s welcoming, motivating and serious about your future.

✨️Ready to forge your craft and your career?✨️

Join The Foundry Acting Studio.

Contact us for more information 
📧 Info@thefoundryactingstudio.com

So yes I understand people being weary of new things but I’m hoping we’ve answered a lot below and again. Like the biggest schools out there.  I am spotlight approved , but I’m also the only independent studio in the U.K. to be SAG recognised and soon to be more . This proves legitimacy. 

So if you’re an actor or starting acting and you want real training , check out the post below. Also if you’re a good person , support other actors and pick people up rather than putting people down. Then you’ll fit perfectly. 

Again . Help each other . Pick each other up. Support each other and be kind to each other . Show new actors that the industry can be a wonderful place . 

Also …. We are the only acting studio making full industry professional feature films and we cast from our students. 

So message us now ….. hope to meet a lot of you soon and keep being fantastic and pushing for that dream
items.title: Hi everyone . I’ve not posted in groups in a long time . I took a break from acting full time almost six years ago when I nearly lost my little girl nine times in one year  to an illness.

🎭 CASTING CALL – New Australian Play in London 🎭

We are casting four roles for an exciting new Australian play, The Beat of the Bronzewing, which will have a showcase reading at the Hen & Chickens Theatre, Islington, on November 12th.

🌪️ About the Play:

When Peggy shows up at Lorraine’s shack in dead-end tropical Australia, she brings an irresistible offer: a one-way ticket out of there. But with a cyclone looming and old wounds resurfacing, can Lorraine be convinced she has nothing to lose?

✨ Longlisted for the Theatre 503 International Playwriting Award 2025, The Beat of the Bronzewing explores the lives of three women in remote Australia, grappling with toxic femininity, domestic abuse, and rural isolation. Set against an evocative tropical landscape, the play is a gripping story of friendship, fear, and survival.

👩‍🎤 The Team

✍️ Writer & Producer: Charlotte Churcher

🎬 Director: Chloe Cattin

🤝 In partnership with the Australian Women’s Club London

📅 Key Dates

Auditions: October 8th (12–5pm) at the Old Red Lion Theatre, Angel, Islington (alternative arrangements available if needed)

Rehearsals: Sunday 9th November (10am–6pm) & Wednesday 12th November (from 2:30pm)

Showcase: Tuesday 12th November at Hen & Chickens Theatre

💷 This is a volunteer opportunity with a £50 contribution towards expenses.

👉 To apply, please complete the form in full.

https://shorturl.at/FmG5A

Casting Call (Non-Union) Paid

Looking for actors to play the role of a client in a simulated therapy session. The video clips will be used in an online training system for counselors and psychologists. The sessions are generally improvised with some prompts or loose scripting.

All ages, all gender expressions/identities, all ethnicities, and persons with disabilities are welcome. We are also very interested in filming with queer couples, interracial couples, or polycules.

Comfortable English fluency is required.

Immediate filming dates are September 23 through 26, but more will occur in the future so please submit if you're interested at all.

Location is downtown Vancouver - Gastown. Pay is 60 cad, duration: 1 hour

Please email phil@skillsetter.com with your headshot and resume. If you've submitted for a past session, you're welcome to submit again.

Hi Everyone!

Sharing from Bryar Casting, in case you haven’t heard yet, **The Reality Directory** is a fresh casting platform connecting real people with amazing opportunities in reality TV, documentaries, commercials looking for everyday folks with incredible stories!

Whether you’re outgoing, quirky, or just your authentic self, this is your chance to be discovered by casting producers looking for people just like you.

Memberships start at $14.99/month. If you’re keen to join or want to learn more, check it out here: www.therealitydirectory.com

And to help you get started, DM us @therealitydirectory with the code **FOUND** for an exclusive discount!

Got questions? Feel free to reach out at casting@therealitydirectory.com or tag friends who might be interested — we’d love to welcome you to the community!

items.text:
Ich suche 1-3 Mitstreiter für ein Straßentheaterprojekt, egal ob Anfänger, erfahrene Amateure oder Profis.

Das Stück (zwischen 2:30 und 15:00 Minuten) soll gemeinsam anhand unserer individuellen Fähigkeiten (zB Tanz, Musik, Akrobatik) entwickelt werden. Grobe Konzepte habe ich schon erarbeitet, genau so wie ich schon einen rechtlichen Rahmen abgeklärt habe.

Mir ist dabei wichtig, dass es humorvoll zugeht, Gag auf Gag wäre ein zentraler Punkt meines Vorstellung, gern gepaart mit einer anachronistischen Optik.

Erfahrung und Möglichkeit im Bereich Bühnenbau und technischer Umsetzung ist reichlich vorhanden.

Ihr solltet in der Umgebung von Aachen wohnen, um regelmässige Proben möglich zu machen.

Neben dem Interesse am Spielen möchte ich den finanziellen Aspekt nicht ganz aussen vor lassen, ich könnte mir langfristig vorstellen, hier einen relevanten Teil meines Einkommens zu bestreiten. Ziel ist zunächst das guerilliamässige Auftreten in Fußgängerzonen, später auch die Teilnahme an internationalen Festivals in Deutschland, Belgien und Frankreich.

Das Ganze soll wirklich langfristig angelegt sein, gern über mehrere Jahre.

Die Fotos habe ich mal angehängt, um ganz grob zu zeigen, in welche Richtung es gehen könnte.

Ich freue mich über alle Anfragen.

items.text:
Hallo, für meinen studentischen, dokumentarischen Kurzfilm suche ich passende Filmmusik, es geht um eine Kneipe.

Budget kann ich nicht anbieten. Aber natürlich Erwähnung im Film.
Der Film wird in einem Berliner Kino laufen zur Premiere und wenn es gut läuft auf Festivals und in weiteren Arthousekinos.

Wer daran interessiert ist gerne mit Link zur Musik kommentieren.

Liebe Grüße aus Berlin

topComments.text:
Der Film soll in Kinos und auf Festivals laufen, dafür bezahlen die Besucher bestimmt auch Eintritt.
Sprich: Einnahmen sind dann da.
Warum kann dann kein Budget für die Filmmusik bezahlt werden?
Sollte ich mit meiner Vermutung daneben liegen, klär mich auf. Danke.

🎭 CASTING DO MUSICALU „CIENIE” 🎶

Szukamy młodych, śpiewających aktorów do zespołu wokalno-aktorskiego nowego musicalu „CIENIE”, którego prapremiera odbędzie się 13.12.2025 w Łodzi! 

Projekt kierowany jest do młodych adeptów sztuki scenicznej (od 16 roku życia).

👉 Aby wziąć udział w castingu, należy przesłać selftape wraz z nagraniem krótkiej piosenki (ok. 1,5 min.).

📩 Zgłoszenia przyjmujemy do 20.09.2025 na adres: musicalcienie@gmail.com

Tylko wybrane osoby zostaną zaproszone na casting stacjonarny, który odbędzie się 27.09.2025 w Łodzi.

🔹 Reżyseria i inscenizacja: Antoniusz Dietzius
🔹 Choreografia: Antonina Grupińska

📅 Terminy prób:
15.10 – 04.12.2025 (czwartki–niedziele)
05.12 – 12.12.2025 (próby całodniowe)

🎟️ Spektakle: 13–19.12.2025

💰 Udział w projekcie płatny.

✨ Nie przegap okazji, aby dołączyć do niezwykłego projektu musicalowego! ✨

📌 Informacja o ochronie danych osobowych:
Przesyłając zgłoszenie, wyrażasz zgodę na przetwarzanie swoich danych osobowych wyłącznie w celu organizacji castingu do musicalu „Cienie”, zgodnie z przepisami RODO. Dane nie będą udostępniane podmiotom trzecim i zostaną usunięte po zakończeniu procesu rekrutacji.

sharedPost.text:
# Karaoke: Pokaż talent… albo dostarcz mema! 

Nowy kanał na YouTube • Kraków – Bielany

Śpiewasz tak, że sąsiad przestaje wierzyć w ciszę nocną?
A może tak, że kot zaczyna klaskać łapką? 
Nieważne! U nas każde gardło ma prawo do sceny.
## O co chodzi?

Wbijasz ➜ śpiewasz ➜ bawisz się ➜ wychodzisz gwiazdą…
…bo nagrywamy **w 4K + dźwięk 5.1** i wrzucamy na **YouTube**! 
A najlepszym **płacimy**. Tak, to nie żart. 
## Dla kogo?
* Dla tych, co mają głos jak miód.
* Dla tych, co mają odwagę jak lew (głos później dogonimy).
* Dla ekip, które potrzebują wspólnej kompromitacji integracji. 
## Co Cię czeka?
*  Mikrofon (nie gryziemy).
*  Hity od „klasyków” po „o matko, kocham ten numer!”.
*  Klip jak z TV: 4K + 5.1 (czyli słychać nawet Twoje „aaa” w tle).
*  Premiera na YouTube — link do chwalenia się, szpanowania i wzruszania cioci.
## FAQ (Fajnie Ale Qurde?)

**A jak fałszuję?**
Spoko, na YouTubie kochamy **autentyczność**. Poza tym: Auto-FUN > Auto-Tune.
**A jak się zestresuję?**
Liczymy do trzech i lecimy jeszcze raz. Mamy niekończące się „bis!”.
**A jak rozwalę system?**
To dopiero problem — będziemy musieli Ci zapłacić. 

 **Gdzie:** Kraków – Bielany
 **Kiedy:** Jak Ci pasuje — dogadamy termin
 **Za ile:** Zaskocz nas talentem (albo jego brakiem) — **najlepszym płacimy**

 **Chcesz wejść na scenę?** Napisz komentarz z hasłem **„KARAOKE 4K”** albo wyślij wiadomość.

Weź mikrofon. Zrób show.
A jeśli nie wyjdzie… trudno — **zrobimy z tego viral**.

My name is Scott, and I work for an award-winning production company that is developing a new documentary series focused on couples in which one of the members was couch surfing, living out of their van, staying with family, or unhoused when the relationship started. #249 casting call - job in Winter 

WE ARE LOOKING FOR THE MOST HANDSOME AND MUSCULAR MALE CIRCUS PERFORMER.

This truly hot man should be able to captivate all female spectators with his entertaining and highly skilled performance. 

Date: 22.11.2025- 18.01.2026
Venue: dinner show in Germany 

Your application with full uncut video, cv, pictures, also headshot, please via email to
booking@mario-danee.de

(For reasons of equality, please no applications from female performers. These positions are already filled.)

No calls please, no whatsapp please!

[🎉](https://emojipedia.org/party-popper)CASTING PAID ROLES FOR PETS AND PET PARENTS [🎉](https://emojipedia.org/party-popper)

Veteos, a local veterinary video production company, is looking for pets for three specific scenes for social media clips for a veterinary financial company. We will be filming within the next month or so in Denver. W9 and signed release required. All scenes are about 2-3 hours of filming. The roles are below:

**Small Dog for a Spa Day** - ($300) Small dog and their pet parent enjoying a spa day. Pup must be able to lie still with a towel over them and on their head with some accessories (see example photo) to show the ultimate puppy spa day! To be considered, please send a video of your small dog lying in a similar position for 5-10 seconds to me via Facebook messenger. 

**Stuffed Animal Lover Dog** - ($300) Dog who LOVES stuffed animals - any stuffed animal! In this scene, we will be making a stuffy "come to life" with a life-size costume of a provided stuffy. Dog must love any and all stuffies, *even if new to them*. To be considered, please send a video of your dog loving their stuffed animals to me via Facebook messenger. 

**Cat Chasing Laser Pointer** - ($300) Cat who can easily follow and loves playing with a laser pointer with their pet parent. Filming location may be rented home or pet parents home depending on the cat's preference and comfort level.To be considered, please send in a video of your cat actively chasing a laser pointer to me via Facebook messenger. 

I can't wait to see your submission!

Sent you one of my pup- will be sending the cat one soon too!

We are casting for a role in our feature film ‘Fairy Dust’!

Please only apply if you fit the brief in the picture and also meet the following criteria:
- Actors must be North Wales based.
- Actors must have the right to work in the UK.
- Actors must be over the age of 18 in real life.
- Must be comfortable wearing full face mask.

Pay is £100 for the day.
Local travel expenses will also be covered & lunch provided.

To apply please send your Spotlight link (or acting CV) as well as your showreel to momentsoffiction@outlook.com

.

items.text:
Hey everyone 👋 I’ve just launched NN5 Talent as part of NN5 Creative Studios. We’re representing actors, social media content creators, and emerging influencers (18+), especially those from underrepresented backgrounds.

I’ve worked in the industry for over a decade, supporting actors who’ve gone on to projects including Top Boy Season 3 (Channel 4/Netflix), The Play That Goes Wrong (Duchess Theatre), The Queen’s Shoes (Feature Film), Ladies Day (Sky Arts ShortFlix), Berlin Station (Paramount/Epix), Tyrant (Fox), The Angel (Netflix), Macbeth (BBC), Flesh and Bone (Edinburgh Headliner/Soho Theatre), Gomorrah (Sky Atlantic), Autopsy (ITV), and Banged Up Abroad (National Geographic).

If you’re looking for representation or want to join a creative hub that’s about real collaboration and growth, check out www.nn5creativestudios.com and drop me an email at create@nn5creativestudios.com.

Let’s make things happen. 🎬✨

CREW CALL – STUDENT SHORT FILM (Unpaid / Non-Union)
Title: Stars Above Us
Shoot Dates: June 5–7, 2026
Location: Bowling Green, KY
We’re seeking passionate and reliable crew members for Stars Above Us, a student drama short film exploring friendship, loss, and mental health. This is a volunteer project—perfect for those looking to gain narrative experience, build credits, and expand reels in a collaborative, professional set environment. All production gear will be provided.

POSITIONS NEEDED
Camera Department
1st Assistant Camera (Focus Puller)

Steadicam Operator

Camera Production Assistants

Grip & Electric (G&E)
Gaffer

Grip & Electric

Swing

Art Department
Production Designer

Art Production Assistant

Production Team
Script Supervisor

Set Production Assistants

Production Manager

Line Producer

Locations Manager

Sound Department
Boom Operator

Utility Sound

Other Roles
Hair Stylist

Makeup Artist

Storyboard Artist

TO APPLY
Please send your information, résumé/reel (if applicable), and the role you’re interested in to:
📧 crewcoordinator.smiletime@gmail.com
Note: If a role is not listed, it has already been filled

items.text:
Rob and I are excited to offer another On Camera Experience for the fall!

6 Classes
October 7th - November 11th 
Tuesdays, 6:30 PM until roughly 9:30 PM
$475 per person (that’s only $80 per class!)

Class Outline
Class One: Getting to know each other, on camera terms and techniques
Class Two: Commercials
Class Three: Comedy
Class Four: Drama
Class Five: Video Games
Class Six: “On Set” - a professional camera op will be filming this class. 

Classes will be a mix of on-camera acting technique and scene study with some acting feedback. All raw footage will be filmed and shared with the students. 

Must join by Tuesday, September 30th.  SPACE IS LIMITED!! To reserve a spot, please contact Sylvia at sylvia@sylviagregorycasting.com

Hope you can be a part of it!

Tuesdays, 6:30 PM until roughly 9:30 PM
$475 per person (that’s only $80 per class!)

Class Outline
Class One: Getting to know each other, on camera terms and techniques
Class Two: Commercials
Class Three: Comedy
Class Four: Drama
Class Five: Video Games
Class Six: “On Set” - a professional camera op will be filming this class. 

Classes will be a mix of on-camera acting technique and scene study with some acting feedback. All raw footage will be filmed and shared with the students. 

Must join by Tuesday, September 30th.  SPACE IS LIMITED!! To reserve a spot, please contact Sylvia at sylvia@sylviagregorycasting.com

Hope you can be a part of it!

items.text:
CASTING MONOLOG – bei Interesse findet am 06. Und 07 November in Berlin – auf  der Probebühne ein Arbeiten mir statt. Bitte melden per e-mail oder Nachricht!

Musik - Schwenk auf ein Sofa oder Bett. Die Schauspielerin erhebt sich aufreizend lächelnd:

*Meine Herren – Ihr Mächtigen dieser Erde – ein jeder Mann erwartet sich ein Fest … mit mir…*

Musik - Überblendung

Die SCHAUSPIELERIN, in einem dünnen seidenen Negligé gekleidet, in ihrer Künstlergarderobe – sie schminkt sich, betrachtet die Papierkrone, die auf dem Schminktisch liegt: …..*ja ja*….*mit mir…*

Die SCHAUSPIELERIN schenkt sich einen Schluck Vodka ein, raucht eine Zigarette zu Ende.  Die SCHAUSPIELERIN betrachtet sich lange im Spiegel – Tränen in den Augen:

*… und…die Mächtigen dieser Erde waschen verlogen ihre Hände in Unschuld …..Wir haben es nicht gewollt. Eine bitterböse Ironie“*

Musik Ende – Überblendung. Die SCHAUSPIELERIN geht einen langen dunklen Gang entlang. An der einen Wand Bilder von Mächtigen Männer: Trump, Putin, Xi, Ghandi, Hitler, Ben Gurion, usw. Auf der anderen Gangseite Bilder von bekannten Frauen der Weltgeschichte. Musik - Überblendung auf leere Bühne – Die SCHAUSPIELERIN in einem bodenlangen Mantel, auf dem Kopf die goldene Papierkrone, grell geschminkt, stark rote Lippen, weißumrandete Augen - in einem Lichtkegel:

*…doch gebt mir ein Königreich als Bühne, Prinzen für die Schauspieler – und ein Haus voller Monarchen! Wie stellt man sonst einen so stolzen Vorwurf dar, wie die Geschichte von Euch - Mächtigen? Meine Herren - Verzeiht – wenn Ihr es schafft, dass schon ein kleiner Tintenklecks auf einem bloßen Stück Papier den Wert einer Million bestimmen kann – so lasst uns fadenscheinige Komödianten für heute den verwegenen Versuch, als Nullen der gewaltigen Totale auf eure Fantasie zu wirken!*

Musik - Überblendung

Die SCHAUSPIELERIN:

*Ja - mit Eurer Fantasie stellt Euch Armeen vor! Und macht aus einem Manne tausend! Doch wenn ich „Pferde“ sage, seht sie, Seht! Da sind sie! Seht sie traben, diese Pferde! Seht ihre Hufe in die weiche Erde schlagen!*

*Meine Herren - nur eure Gedanken sind´s, die meine Könige in Gold und Purpur kleiden müssen, sie hin und her versetzen. Nur Eure Fantasie springt über Zeiten weg und kann den Lauf von Jahren umdrehen, wie ein Stundenglas.*

*Bildet Euch ein, da wären tausend Schiffe! Und seht wie mächtig ihre Brust sich durch den stolzen Schaum des Meeres bricht, vom unsichtbaren Wind gejagt!*

*Und seht den flinken Burschen dort mit seiner Lunte!*

*Jetzt zündet er die teuflische Kanone- und alles bricht vor Euch zusammen!*

*Und weiter! Versetzt euch wie ein Blitz aufs Schlachtfeld!*

*Seht meine Schwerter tanzen und sich in eurer Feinde Brust versenken!*

*Ja, sie sind aus Blech und schadhaft, lächerlich. Aber sie tanzen nicht zum Spaß: die Schlacht ist ernst, wahrhafter als die Wirklichkeit! Ich bitte aber den Historiker unter Ihnen – in aller Demut - die Daten, Zahlen und die Fakten nicht mit dem Maßstab der exakten Wissenschaft zu messen. Die Geschichte von Euch mächtigen Herren lässt sich nicht erzählen.  Nur in ihrer Ganzheit ist sie wahr, und wo sie wahr ist, ist sie nicht exakt! Denn nichts erhebt sich von der Erde, dass nicht die Zeit mit ihrer Sichel niedermäht! Im Gegenteil……ich baut vor Eurer Tür ein Weidenhüttchen und sänge Lieder – laut - der Liebe! Und wenn die Musik der Liebe Nahrung - so spiel ich weiter, weiter bis zum Überdruss. Meine Herren - Ihr Mächtigen dieser Erde: Schießt nicht auf mich Komödiantin!*

Mit einem Lächeln verbeugt sich die SCHAUSPIELERIN – dann plötzlich ein Schuss.  Die SCHAUSPIELERIN sinkt langsam zu Boden. Blackout.

# **CASTING-AUFRUF – UGC-Videodreh für Immobilienprojekt in LEIPZIG // FREITAG 26.09.2025**
Drehort: LEIPZIG

Drehtag: 26.09.2025 - 10.00 Uhr

Geplanter Drehzeitraum: halber Drehtag (4–5 Stunden)
Schauspielhonorar: 500 € pauschal

Was wir drehen:

Für unseren Kunden, einen Immobilienunternehmen aus LEIPZIG, produzieren wir 25 kurze UGC-Videos (User Generated Content) für Social Media & Online-Ads. Die Videos sind authentisch gesprochene Clips, die direkt in die Kamera eingesprochen werden – klar, sympathisch, ruhig.

Skriptlänge pro Video: 40–60 Sekunden, ein Teleprompter ist vor Ort – keine Auswendiglernerei notwendig.

Gesucht werden:
* 1 Schauspielerin & 1 Schauspieler
* Alter: 28–40 Jahre
* Look: authentisch, gepflegt, urban-professionell – ein natürlicher „Young Professional“-Vibe (Think: Start-up, Immobilienberater, Creator mit Vertrauensausstrahlung)
* Sprache: Hochdeutsch, sichere Sprechweise, gute Artikulation
* Erfahrung mit Kamera & Social Media Ads von Vorteil, aber keine Voraussetzung

Über uns:

Wir sind die IMMO 4.0 GmbH, ein Performance-Marketing-Unternehmen aus Heidelberg.

Wir entwickeln Marketingkampagnen für Immobilienvertriebe, Bauträger und Kapitalanlageprodukte im DACH-Raum – und setzen dabei bewusst auf echtes, greifbares Storytelling mit professionellem UGC-Content.

Das bieten wir Dir:
* 500 € Pauschalgage
* Teleprompter + eingespielte Crew vor Ort
* Styling & Text-Input durch uns (kein Kostüm notwendig, clean/professionell reicht)
* Reelfähige Referenz für Deine Mappe
* Zusammenarbeit mit erfahrenem Videoteam in lockerer, produktiver Atmosphäre

Bewerbung:

Bitte sende uns bis asap Deine Bewerbung mit:
* 2–3 aktuellen Bildern oder Showreel
* Kurzprofil (Name, Alter, Standort)
* Optional: Link zu Instagram / Agenturseite / Eigenen Reels
* Betreff: „UGC-Videodreh LEIPZIG – Vorname Nachname“

Bewerbung bitte per WhatsApp an: +49 172 7042469

(Phillip Kirillov - IMMO4.0 GmbH)

Hinweis:

Die finalen Produktionen erscheinen im Rahmen einer Online-Marketingkampagne für den Bereich Kapitalanlage-Immobilien. Seriös, hochwertig, glaubwürdig.

Wir freuen uns auf Deine Bewerbung – let’s create!

Dein Team von IMMO 4.0 GmbH

items.text:
Für meinen historisch-romantischen Kurzfilm (1–3 Minuten) suche ich eine Schauspielpartnerin (25–30 Jahre) aus Ulm oder Umgebung.

Über das Projekt:
Es handelt sich um ein Herzensprojekt, nicht bezahlt, dafür mit viel Leidenschaft. Wir drehen eine Szene im Stil klassischer Historienromanzen – Spaziergang, Dialoge voller Tiefe, ein erster Kuss und eine leidenschaftliche Kaminszene.

Wichtig:

Keine Scheu oder Scham vor einem Kuss und einer leidenschaftlichen Szene (ästhetisch, stilvoll, keine Nacktheit).

Du musst keine ausgebildete Schauspielerin sein – entscheidend ist deine Spielfreude, Leidenschaft und der Mut, dich auf die Rolle einzulassen.

🚨URGENT CASTING CALL🚨

Project Title: SIO: Origins
Production Company: Museboxx M&F
Location: Darbyshire???? TBA (UK-based production)
Deadline: Urgent

Role: Co-Starring Leads – Names TBA
We’re casting for two dynamic male actors to take on a co-starring leading roles in our upcoming production, SIO: Origins, part of the larger SIO universe. The roles are emotionally charged and physically demanding, featuring performance across acting, dance, singing, and occasional stunt choreography. For these roles, We do have places for the characters to appear on the final episode of SIO:Echoes of the SIX - which has been airing throughout this year online. And to be a part of other SIO series', including live performances and other Muaeboxx projects.

Character Traits & Requirements:

• Sexuality: Gay & Bisexual
• Age: 26-28
• Height: 5ft 7 to 6ft
• Performance Abilities: Singer, Dancer, Acting and Rap
• Comfortable of doing own Stunts
• Comfortable with doing Gymnastics
• No piercings/jewelry

• Must be available for Live Performances

Previous experience in emotionally intense roles is a bonus

Payment & Contract:
Budget is currently being finalised. Payment details will be discussed at a later stage and confirmed in actor contracts. This will be a credited role with potential for expanded involvement in future series.

To Apply:
Send an email to museboxxmfcasting@gmail.com to send the following: Submit headshot, showreel (if available).
Audition scripts and details will be provided upon application.

If you have any issues with contacting the email above, please don't hesitate to contact our other email below - wintersxperia@gmail.com

More details about the projects will be discussed throughout the Audition process.

items.text:
Thank you so much for welcoming me to your group!  

I'm a NYC and NJ native, now living in Florida, pursuing acting work to support my film project.  I have significant experience in films.  Supported directors and producers.  I had 5 years as an extra for feature films such as El Cantante, Be Kind/Rewind, and traveled to audition for theatre and short films. Beyond acting, I'm an editor, photographer, and former Spectrum Television production intern with five years of hands-on experience with equipment, and in 2019 created my first show in Western Connecticut, Channel 192, "Spoken Voices."  A passionate advocate against domestic violence. I bring dedication, creativity, and authenticity to every role, and you can find me on FaceBook, "Maribel Brooks" for future auditioning!

items.text:
Casting Call – Mandlig skuespiller/statist søges

Vi er et hold på seks studerende fra VIA Film & Transmedia i Aarhus. I forbindelse med et skoleprojekt samarbejder vi med designer Fie Nielsen og hendes studie, Fjör Studio, om branding af en ny tøjkollektion.

Kollektionen udforsker, hvad det vil sige at være mand i dag, og leger med udtryk, der udfordrer de traditionelle forestillinger om styrke, følelser og identitet.

Vi søger en mand i alderen 17–30 år, ca. 180 cm høj, almindelig af bygning og med tøjstørrelse small–medium.

Praktisk info
 Optagelserne finder sted i Skanderborg
 Mandag den 22/9
 Kl. 09.00–17.00

Projektet er frivilligt, men vi sørger selvfølgelig for mad, drikke, transport – og en sjov oplevelse samt muligheden for at få et spændende projekt på CV’et.

Kontakt Fredrik på (+45) 2285 1519 eller 354549@via.dk, hvis du er interesseret. 

Vi glæder os til at høre fra dig!

Kontakt Fredrik pả (+45) 2285 1519 eller 354549@via.dk 354549 @via.dk hvis du er interesseret. VIA University College'

items.text:
Hej 

Mit navn er Luca Giusio 
Jeg er 17 år 
Og bor i Kolding/vejle 

Jeg laver lige det her opslag fordi jeg rigtig gerne vil være skuespiller og elsker det med film og skuespil og alt i den dur 
Jeg er en passioneret og energisk person, der elsker at udtrykke mig gennem både drama og humor. 

Jeg har erfaring med:

Har været en del af dystopia i Vejle siden 2020
Har gået til teater i 2 år og været med i 2 forestillinger 
Har lavet små kortfilm og min egen spillefilm igennem min barndom 

Højde: 175
Sprog: Dansk/engelsk 
Jeg er dedikeret lærenem – og så elsker jeg at arbejde kreativt sammen med andre

Tak for at I tager jer tid til at læse med 

jeg håber at høre fra jer

Bedste hilsner Luca Giusio

🎅🏼 CHRISTMAS CASTING 🎅🏼

We're on the lookout for a jolly, warm-hearted Father Christmas to bring festive magic to life at one of Liverpool’s top attractions this November & December!

✨ The Role: You’ll be the star of our magical grotto experience, meeting families, chatting with children, and spreading Christmas cheer. A twinkle in the eye, a hearty "Ho Ho Ho", and a love of all things festive are a must!

📍 Location: Prescot, just outside of Liverpool 
📅 Dates: Select dates throughout Nov & December (22 dates)
💰 Competitive day rate + full costume and training provided

📧 To apply, please send a short intro, recent photo/headshot, and any relevant experience to Info@LaughingBulldogEvents.co.uk with the subject line "Father Christmas Casting - Liverpool".

items.text:
**PAID OPPORTUNITY FOR UK BUSINESS OWNERS!**

Are you a business owner with a captivating story and a knack for on-camera presence? Fancy getting paid to promote your company?

**Casper Black Casting** & **Quickbooks** are seeking **dynamic entrepreneurs** of all sizes to participate in a series of fun and engaging YouTube business-based game shows!

We're looking for business owners, from startup freelancers to those generating seven-figure revenues, who are comfortable discussing and even debating their ventures. This is a fantastic opportunity to pitch your business, share your experiences, and potentially gain valuable exposure.

**What we're looking for:**

*Business Owners of All Types: *From individual freelancers to established businesses with significant revenue.

*Comfortable on Camera*: You'll be the star of the show, so a natural and confident on-screen demeanor is essential. *Memorable personalities are welcome! *We want 10/10 out of the box personalities.

*Willing to Discuss Your Business and Revenue:* Be prepared to openly share insights into your operations and financial journey.

**Shoot Details:**

Location: West London

Duration: Approximately 2-3 hours

Timeframe: Early October (likely 2nd or 3rd October)

If you're ready to showcase your business and your personality, we want to hear from you!

**Please email casper@casperblackcasting.com with the answers to these questions:**
1. We require that you are a business owner. Please specify your annual revenue:
* £0-£100k per year
* £100k-£1m per year
* £1m+ per year
2. Please describe your business in 1-2 sentences.
3. Kindly detail your previous on-camera experience.
4. Please send a link to your website if applicable.
5. Kindly share your contact number.

**Paid Studio Gig – Surrey, BC (1–2 days, max 7 hrs/day)**

Hey Vancouver actors! We’re producing a batch of short videos for our brand (YouTube, Reels, TikTok, Facebook) and are looking for a confident on-camera presenter to record with us at our Surrey studio.

**What it is:**
* 1–2 studio days, max **7 hours per day**
* Scripted teleprompter reads + a few simple pickups/B-roll
* We provide the studio, teleprompter, and all gear
* **Contract provided** and **payment in full on wrap**

**You:** Comfortable on camera, friendly, clear delivery, can self-report to Surrey.

**Dates/Rate:** negotiable and flexable 

If you’re interested, please fill out this form, https://form.jotform.com/252610493666057 

with:
* Headshot + reel/links
* Your availability in **[date range]**
* A quick note confirming you can get to Surrey

Thanks! Excited to meet some local talent.

*What if you uncovered something dark buried in a past life?*

Migraine is a psychological-spiritual thriller short film, and we are currently casting background for a **1950s jazz club scene.**

**Details:**
* Age: **19+**
* Gender: **Any **
* Ethnicity:** Any** 
* Location: **Greater Vancouver Area** 
* Rate:** Volunteer. We are a low-budget indie film hyper-focused on quality.** 
* Date: **Sept. 25 or 28**

*please let us know if you available for one or both dates

To submit please send us your name and contact info at **migraine.shortfilm@gmail.com**

We look forward to working with you!

‼️NORTHWEST BIPOC ENTERTAINERS‼️

We are actively seeking talented BIPOC performers to bring beloved characters such as; Princess Tiana, Mulan, Mirabel, Jasmine, Moana, iconic Korean figures and more to life through engaging and authentic performances.

To our company representation matters! We are committed to celebrating the rich cultural heritage of these characters embodied by casting performers who reflect their backgrounds. Whether you're an experienced entertainer or a passionate newcomer, if you have a love for storytelling, performance, and creating magical moments for audiences of all ages, we invite you to join us in inspiring the next generation through inclusive and empowering portrayals.

Please PM Ever Enchanted Events or email everenchantedevent@gmail.com with a headshot, CV and a little about yourself and your background🥰⭐️

# 🎬 **NAGRANIA KRAKÓW **🎬

Do realizacji ciekawego filmu na jeden z największych kanałów YouTube w Polsce poszukujemy osoby chętnej wziąć udział w projekcie. Zadaniem aktora będzie odegranie krótkiej sceny z elementami improwizacji. 
## 🔎 **Kogo szukamy?**
* Mężczyzna w wieku 25-50 lat
* Łysa głowa (nie wymagana, ale mile widziana 🙂)
* Dystans do siebie
* Swoboda przed kamerą (doświadczenie mile widziane, ale niekonieczne)
## ℹ️ **INFORMACJE**
* Lokalizacja: Kraków
* Termin: 17.09.25
* Czas trwania: 1 godzina

** Jesteś chętny? – odezwij się w wiadomości prywatnej, a prześlę więcej szczegółów! **

📍  WARSZAWA
🎬 ❗️. NOWY FILM FABULARNY, reż. Janusz Zaorski❗️.
📆 1 PAŹDZIERNIKA, ŚRODA
Na plan najnowszego filmu KINOWEGO
❗️w reżyserii JANUSZA ZAORSKIEGO❗️
poszukujemy statystów z Warszawy i okolic.

📆 1 PAŹDZIERNIKA, ŚRODA
CZASY WSPÓŁCZESNE
Dziewczynki i Chłopcy w wieku 5-6 lat jako
- przedszkolaki
Preferowane dzieci z uprawnieniami Państwowej Inspekcji Pracy (PIP)
Panie w wieku 25-40 lat jako
- przedszkolanki

📆 1 PAŹDZIERNIKA, ŚRODA
❗️ czas akcji 1948 ROK ❗️
Panie i Panowie w wieku 18-60 lat jako
- widzowie w kinie
UWAGA! Do tej sceny wymagany jest odpowiedni wizerunek i klasyczne fryzury. Brak tatuaży w widocznych miejscach.
Panie włosy naturalne lub farbowane na naturalny kolor, brak makijażu permanentnego, tipsów , hybryd, piercingu i zabiegów medycyny estetycznej  itp..
Panowie równomierna długość włosów,
❗️bez współczesnego wygolenia boków głowy❗️.

Proszę o przemyślane zgłoszenia.
UWAGA! 
Reżyser wybiera na podstawie zdjęć.
Rozpatrywane będą tylko prawidłowe i pełne zgłoszenia.
Zgłoszenia::
fabula@sceneria.com.pl
W zgłoszeniu proszę zamieścić:
Imię, nazwisko, wiek, numer tel., miasto zamieszkania, aktualne zdjęcie twarzy i sylwetki
Temat: 01.10. PRZEDSZKOLE
          ❗️01.10. KINO 1948 ROK ❗️

Hej!
Poszukuję epizodystów do serialu Lombard:

(nagrania we Wrocławiu)

24.09
Chlor - (ok 64l), zniszczony alkoholik, żyje samotnie w biedzie. Posiada zadłużone mieszkanie po rodzicach. Podpisuje pełnomocnictwo, pozwalając Glebie i Bukwie dysponować lokalem w zamian za pomoc z długami. Podtruwany izopropanolem, staje się ofiarą „gangu trucicieli”.

27.09
BOREK – (ok 25l) kolega Mirka, wesoły chłopak, kombinator, lekkoduch, sympatyczny łobuz…

26.09
Matka, ok. (40 lat) aktywna, wysportowana, pogodna. Łagodzi konflikty między tyranizującym mężem a buntującą się córką.

23.09
SĄSIAD – (50-letni mężczyzna mający działkę na tym samym ROD-zie, nieco grubawy, umiarkowanie atrakcyjny

23.09
KLIENT – klient Niny, facet w garniaku ok 50-tki, zwykły facet, nie za piękny, ale też nie za brzydki.

Zgłoszenie proszę przesłać na przemek.edwinfilm@gmail.com lub na PRIV

Hello all, this is another post for a different student film happening on Auraria Campus. I am not involved in this one, I am posting to this group for the producer since he is not on Facebook. So if you are interested in this one please contact the producer. 

Producer- Brennan Jones bjones89@msudenver.edu 

Production Title- The Cost of Greed 

Production Dates- Exact dates are not set but filming will be in October 

Logline- Peter and Henry are sent on a treasure hunt to a house that is believed to be abandoned. Where they then discover it's not a treasure hunt after all and they must face their greed. Either take the treasure or leave empty handed. 

Peter (19-25) Male 

Peter has a moral compass that he deals with during this film. He wants to do the right thing and in the end that pays off for him. 

Henry (19-25) Male 

Henry is a billionaire with no need for more money, however that does not stop him from thinking he needs more. He is corrupt and in the end karma gets to him. 

Audition Dates- September 18th-September 29th

Audition Location- Email-Self Tape

This is a student film for a final project therefore this film is non paid and non union.

Contact Email- bjones89@msudenver.edu 

Must contact the producer to be consider for the role. Once you contact Brennan he will send you the audition material.

items.text:
Hello, we are currently casting for a student film on Auraria Campus! 

Producers- Isabella Coronado & Alanagh Finken 

Production Title- Normal Activity 

Production Dates- We don't have exact dates yet but we do know that we are filming in October. 

Logline- A mocumentary following a college's ghost hunting group as they prepare to explore a haunted local brewery's basement where a spirit has resided for the past thirty years. 

Alex (19-25) Male 

Alex is the leader of the ghost hunting group, he is very enthusiastic. He is clearly the one that is most devoted to this group. 

Chelsea (19-25) Female 

Chelsea is your typical girly girl likes being on camera but does not care about the club she is in. She is pretending to so that the club can get funding for the "haunted (not haunted) hot springs". 

Tommy (19-25) Male 

Tommy is very clearly apart of the club because he has eyes for Chelsea, he could not care less otherwise. 

Vera (19-25) Female 

Vera is Alex's sister and is only there because Alex believes they needed a fourth member and basically bribed Vera to join by saying she could borrow his car whenever she wants. 

Gary (45-55) Male 

Gary is the nightwatchmen for the brewery basement. He is very encouraging to Alex with his ghost hunting group. However that encouragement is not for reasons you think, Gary has a secret. 

Documentarian (20-30) Male, Female, Non Binary 

The documentarian is not really shown on camera, however they play a very important role. They are the voice we hear throughout the film asking questions to our characters, and making sarcastic and humorous remarks because they like everyone except Alex, thinks this club is utterly ridicules. 

Audition Dates- September 18th-September 29th 

Audition Location- Email-Self Tape 

This is a student film for a final project therefore this film is non paid and non union. 

**Contact Email- afinken1@msudenver.edu | icoronad@msudenver.edu **

**You must email both producers. Email the producers about your interest in the role and then we will send you the audition piece for your self tape. You must email to be considered, Facebook Messages does not count. **

Kristian Beck - Kölsche Tön! Seid ihr bereit für den „❤️KÖLSCHEN❤️“ Musikgenuss?

In diesem Clip präsentiere ich euch - elf kurze Hörproben meines "Special Albums" - Kölsch trifft Schlager. Ein Mix aus rockigen, poppigen, karnevalistischen und weihnachtlichen Klängen!

Egal ob beim Feiern im Karneval oder beim gemütlichen Beisammensein – hier ist für jeden etwas dabei!

Kristian Beck - Kölsche Tön! Seid ihr bereit für den „❤️KÖLSCHEN❤️“ Musikgenuss?

In diesem Clip präsentiere ich euch - elf kurze Hörproben meines "Special Albums" - Kölsch trifft Schlager. Ein Mix aus rockigen, poppigen, karnevalistischen und weihnachtlichen Klängen!

Egal ob beim Feiern im Karneval oder beim gemütlichen Beisammensein – hier ist für jeden etwas dabei!

🎬 ✨ مسابقة نجم كيمت ميديا برودكشن ✨🎬

لو عندك موهبة التمثيل وبتحلم تبقى نجم ⭐️ … الفرصة جاتلك مع شركة كمت ميديا برودكشن!

📌 شارك في مسابقتنا الخاصة وقدّم فيديو تمثيلي مدته من 3 دقائق لحد 6 دقائق، وأظهر فيه قدراتك
#محتوى_المسابقه ؛
 1. الدراما الإنسانية

قصص عن العلاقات (أب–ابنه، أم–بنتها، أصحاب).

 2. مواقف بتبين قيم زي التضحية، الرحمة، الغدر أو الصداقة.قصة نجاح قصيرة.

 3. شخص بيواجه تحدي وبيكسب أو يتعلم درس.•

🔹 شروط المشاركة:

.1 ان يكون مدة الفيديو من  3 – 6 دقائق

.2 ان يكون جوده الفيديو Hd بحد ادنى

3. ان يكون الفيديو متبع لمعاير المجتمع 

4- آخر موعد للتقديم: (10/10/2025)

💰 الجايزة الكبرى: 50,000 جنيه كاش للفائز الأول!
غير إنك هتاخد فرصة حقيقية تبدأ مشوارك الفني وتشارك في أعمالنا القادمة 🎥

📩 التواصل عبر رسائل الصفحه لتوجيهكم بخطوات الاشتراك 

#ملحوظه_هامه ؛ الاشتراك في المسابقه مجانا بدون أي رسوم 

🏆 يمكن تكون أنت النجم اللي مستنيينه!

#كيمت_ميديا_برودكشن #مسابقة_التمثيل #اكتشاف_المواهب

items.text:
**CASTING-AUFRUF – UGC-Videodreh für Immobilienprojekt in Heidelberg // Donnerstag 25.09.2025**
 
Drehort: Heidelberg // Bahnstadt

Drehtag: 25.09.2025 - 10.00 Uhr
 
Geplanter Drehzeitraum: halber Drehtag (4–5 Stunden)
Schauspielhonorar: 500 € pauschal
Was wir drehen:

Für unseren Kunden, einen Immobilienunternehmen aus Hamburg, produzieren wir 25 kurze UGC-Videos (User Generated Content) für Social Media & Online-Ads. Die Videos sind authentisch gesprochene Clips, die direkt in die Kamera eingesprochen werden – klar, sympathisch, ruhig.

Skriptlänge pro Video: 40–60 Sekunden, ein Teleprompter ist vor Ort – keine Auswendiglernerei notwendig.
 
Gesucht werden:
* 1 Schauspielerin & 1 Schauspieler
* Alter: 28–40 Jahre
* Look: authentisch, gepflegt, urban-professionell – ein natürlicher „Young Professional“-Vibe (Think: Start-up, Immobilienberater, Creator mit Vertrauensausstrahlung)
* Sprache: Hochdeutsch, sichere Sprechweise, gute Artikulation
* Erfahrung mit Kamera & Social Media Ads von Vorteil, aber keine Voraussetzung
Über uns:

Wir sind die IMMO 4.0 GmbH, ein Performance-Marketing-Unternehmen aus Heidelberg.

Wir entwickeln Marketingkampagnen für Immobilienvertriebe, Bauträger und Kapitalanlageprodukte im DACH-Raum – und setzen dabei bewusst auf echtes, greifbares Storytelling mit professionellem UGC-Content.

Das bieten wir Dir:
* 500 € Pauschalgage
* Teleprompter + eingespielte Crew vor Ort
* Styling & Text-Input durch uns (kein Kostüm notwendig, clean/professionell reicht)
* Reelfähige Referenz für Deine Mappe
* Zusammenarbeit mit erfahrenem Videoteam in lockerer, produktiver Atmosphäre

Bewerbung:

Bitte sende uns bis asap Deine Bewerbung mit:
* 2–3 aktuellen Bildern oder Showreel
* Kurzprofil (Name, Alter, Standort)
* Optional: Link zu Instagram / Agenturseite / Eigenen Reels
* Betreff: „UGC-Videodreh Heidelberg – Vorname Nachname“

Bewerbung bitte per WhatsApp an: +49 172 7042469

(Phillip Kirillov - IMMO4.0 GmbH)

Hinweis:

Die finalen Produktionen erscheinen im Rahmen einer Online-Marketingkampagne für den Bereich Kapitalanlage-Immobilien. Seriös, hochwertig, glaubwürdig.

Wir freuen uns auf Deine Bewerbung – let’s create!

Dein Team von IMMO 4.0 GmbH

items.text:
Casting Call – Mandlig skuespiller/statist søges

Vi er et hold på seks studerende fra VIA Film & Transmedia i Aarhus. I forbindelse med et skoleprojekt samarbejder vi med designer Fie Nielsen og hendes studie, Fjör Studio, om branding af en ny tøjkollektion.

Kollektionen udforsker, hvad det vil sige at være mand i dag, og leger med udtryk, der udfordrer de traditionelle forestillinger om styrke, følelser og identitet.

Vi søger en mand i alderen 17–30 år, ca. 180 cm høj, almindelig af bygning og med tøjstørrelse small–medium.

Praktisk info
 Optagelserne finder sted i Skanderborg
 Mandag den 22/9
 Kl. 09.00–17.00

Projektet er frivilligt, men vi sørger selvfølgelig for mad, drikke, transport – og en sjov oplevelse samt muligheden for at få et spændende projekt på CV’et.

Kontakt Fredrik på (+45) 2285 1519 eller 354549@via.dk, hvis du er interesseret. 

Vi glæder os til at høre fra dig!

items.text:
Casting Call – Voice Actors (Ulønnet)

Hej alle,

Vi er et hold fra Masterclass på Potemkin – Den Jyske Filmskole, som er i postproduktion på et spændende projekt. Derfor søger vi nu stemmeskuespillere til to roller.

Logline:

En håbefuld, men overset filminstruktør får chancen i en branche styret af sequels og profit – og må vælge mellem at gå på kompromis med sine værdier eller med sin karriere.

Vi søger:

 • Kvindestemme – til at udlevere en Robertpris (kort ceremoniel replik - tænk "And the Oscar goes to..."). Alder er underordnet.

 • Mandestemme – til rollen som producer (kort telefondialogscene). Alder underordnet, da det er stemmen vi søger, men vi søger i omfanget af 25-39 år. 

Praktisk:

 • Projektet er ulønnet, men alle medvirkende bliver krediteret i filmen.
        • Lydoptagelsen vil foregå i Potemkins lydstudie på Fredens Torv 3A, Aarhus C 8000.

Er du interesseret? Send mig en mail på simonthomaslange@gmail.com med en kort besked, eventuelt som lydoptaglese, så får du flere detaljer :)

Vi glæder os til at høre fra dig!

items.text:
Hi everyone,
I’m Callum Foley 24, an actor based in Nottingham. I’ve recently been working on background and student film projects, and I’m keen to get involved in short films, indie projects, and commercials to build on-screen experience.

items.text:
Har lige nu flere filmproduktioner, hvor der er brug for statister..
Søger folk inden for 60 minutters kørsel fra Århus.

#1
Uge 40 - Reklamefilm Østjylland

Location: Malling

Søger: Mand + Kvinde i alderen 55-65 år. Skal spille et modent par. Kan søges individuelt - men privat relation foretrækkes.

Søger: Ung familie (Far, mor + barn ca 5 år). Skal have relation.

Tid: 1/2 dag

Lønnet

#2
November - reklamefilm Norden

Location: Østjylland

Søger: Alle typer (skal bruge 10-15 personer) - med mod og lyst til statistrolle + at danse simpel koreografi i rollen. Danseerfaring er ikke et krav .

Søger: Gymnaster/showdansere/HipHop alder 16-40 år, der skal lave mere kompliceret koreografi. Gerne en dansegruppe (mix M/K), der kender hinanden

Tid: 1-2 optagedage

Lønnet

Send besked til kontakt@kaiserwetter.dk med note om hvilken rolle du søger, foto, navn, alder og hvor i Jylland du bor.

items.text:
🎬 CASTING: Familie søges til reklamefilm 🌟 Lønnet 

Vi leder efter en skandinavisk mand og kvinde i slut 30’erne/start 40’erne samt en pige på 7–8 år til en varm og troværdig reklameproduktion for en detailkæde. Gerne søges som en samlet familie, men ikke nødvendigt 

📍 Optagelse: cirka 4 timer 
Lokation: Herning  
📅 Dato: 7 oktober 
🎥 Brug: Sociale medier, TV, biograf og online i Danmark, Sverige, Norge og Finland
🖼️ Stillbilleder: Bruges online og evt. på print i kædens fysiske butikker
⏳ Brugsret: 3 år med mulighed for forlængelse (brugen af reklamen er dog sæson præget, så ville i vintermånederne) 

Udstråling: Glad og frisk udstråling, og med evnen til at skabehygge.
Samspillet mellem de to voksne og datteren er bærende, og det er derfor vigtigt at de voksne er gode med børn og at barnet er skuespils vant.

📩 Interesseret? Send et par billeder + kort præsentation eller materiale fra tidligere projekter til [sille.schnoor13@gmail.com]
Skriv gerne “Familie casting” i emnefeltet.

topComments.text: Tidsrum og løn?
Ærgerligt det ikke foregår i Kbh

🎭ADVERT CASTING BRIEF🎭

Looking for the below Actors:

* 1 x Businesswoman, white, 40s, fit, redhead (banker vibes) - send a 30 sec video speaking Posh English Accent 

* 1 x Businessman, white, 40s, blonde (banker vibes) - Send 30 sec video speaking posh English accent 

* 1 x white woman to be the Driver, 20s (non-speaking)

* 5 x Japanese men, 30s – 60s (attractive, good looking) - send a 30sec video reacting and “sounding” Japanese

* 1 x Japanese woman, 20s (non-speaking)

* 2 x White men, late 40s (successful businesspeople, but outdoorsy types. Strapping men) - send a 30 sec video speaking Good Australian accent. – “Yeah mate!”

* 1 x Black man (Driver), 40s/50s

* 2 x Indian women, 1 x 30s/40s and 1 x 50s. English speaking - send 30sec video speaking English in authentic Indian/Mumbai accent

* 1x Indian man, 30s. English speaking. - send a 30 sec video speaking English in authentic Indian accent
* 2 x Arab men, 30s & 40s (groomed facial hair – beards don’t have to be long or bushy – the current trend is quite short and well-shaped) - send a 30 sec video speaking English but with a natural Saudi / Arab / Gulf accent

* 2x Arab men (non-speaking)

* 2 x Italian men, 40s and 50s (dashing or handsome) - send 30sec video speaking good Italian.

* 1 x Italian woman, 30s (striking or attractive) - send a 30sec video speaking good Italian 

* 1 x Portuguese man 40s (darker-haired – maybe a curl, warmer/olive-skinned, maybe dense facial hair… a Mediterranean vibe) - send a 30sec video speaking Portuguese and English

* 1x Black South African man, 40s (charismatic businessman vibe, the air of trust and success) - Send a 30sec video speaking good English

* 1 x Portuguese woman, 30s + 1 x Black South African woman, 30s  (non-speaking)

* 1 x French man, white, 40s (mischievous, urban, effortlessly stylish, and slightly romantic… a sense of refinement, wit, and nonchalant charm) - send a 30sec video in Good French accent “C’est magnifique!”

* 1 x Chinese man 50s/60s (professional-looking guy. Well-groomed) - send a 30sec video in a distinct Chinese accent

- Speaking Role: Rate is R4000
- Non-Speaking Role: Rate is R2000

DEADLINE: WEDNESDAY (17/09/2025) at 5pm. 

Thank you 
LJ Talent Casting 💫

items.text:
LOOKING FOR 2 MEN (preferably BASS or BARITONE), 1 WOMAN (preferably ALTO) who can dance and have the ability to harmonize, for our upcoming Holiday Show. 

Ensemble Stage is a professional theater located in Banner Elk, NC which is situated in the Blue Ridge Mtns. in western North Carolina. Our facility consists of over 8000 sq. ft. which includes a 99-seat performance auditorium.

About 90 total hours (rehearsals + performances), no two-show days, no 10-out-of-12's, no more than 3 performances per week (7 total performances). 

contract runs 11/14 thru 12/20.  Fyi- we have no rehearsals Wednesday thru Saturday of Thanksgiving week so you have an opportunity to go be with family if you choose. 

Pay is $260 per week for five weeks (comes to around $14 per hour of actual rehearsal and performance time). Housing is fully provided(includes full kitchen, washer/dryer, wifi, free parking, individual bedroom, no more than two share a bathroom (but usually private) , etc.  Also, no smoking, and no pets (or service animals) are allowed in any housing. 

Round-trip travel reimbursed at $0.25 per mile

Finally,since we are located in the mountains, and since Ensemble Stage does not have a "company car" available for use, having your own vehicle while here is pretty much a necessity. There really is no such thing as walking to the store or to the theatre.

If interested please respond to info@ensemblestage.com, subject- CMAS AUDITIONS. I will then send you details and parameters for you to prepare a video callback audition to be submitted.

attachments.ocrText: No photo description available.

items.text:
📢Volunteers Wanted - Videographers! Liverpool Mystery Event📢

CAJ Productions is looking for 2 more reliable volunteers to help with a one-off mystery stunt in Liverpool City Centre on Saturday 20th September 2025.

It's part of a brand-new UK theatre tour coming in 2026, and this will be one of our headline public marketing stunts. 

The role is simple, but really important:

. Filming the event (reactions) on a phone (2 people required)

What you'll get:

. Travel expenses covered

. Be part of an unusual, exciting event that's going to get a lot of attention

. Something different to talk about (and looks great on a CV for anyone in events, film, or theatre)

If you're free, reliable, and up for being part of something mysterious and fun, drop me a message here or comment below and I'll share the details.

Thanks! 

Charlie

items.text:
🎃Halloween acting job opportunity🎃

🎃 Join the Cast of Halloween at Winstanley Park! 👻✨

We’re searching for fun, energetic, and family-friendly performers to bring the magic of Halloween to life at Winstanley Park’s half-term events this October!

Event Details:
 • 📅 Event Dates: 25th – 31st October
 • ⏰ Times: 10:00am – 4:30pm daily
 • 💷 Run Rate: £1050 for the full event

Rehearsals (attendance required):
 • 🗓️ Rehearsal: 17th October
 • 🗓️ Dress Run: 21st October

What We’re Looking For:
 • Friendly, engaging performers who love interacting with children and families
 • Ability to stay in character and create a magical, seasonal atmosphere
 • Great storytelling and improvisation skills
 • Previous experience in theatre, children’s entertainment, or immersive events is a plus
 • ✅ Must hold a valid DBS check

What You’ll Get:
 • A competitive run rate
 • The chance to create unforgettable Halloween memories for families
 • A supportive, creative team environment in the beautiful Winstanley Park

👻 Whether you’re a mischievous witch, a cheeky pumpkin sprite, or a friendly ghost, we want to hear from you!

How to Apply:
📩 Please send:
 • Your CV
 • A 30-second video of you telling a short ghost story
to: RegallyRoyalParties@yahoo.com

Audition Day (in-person):
📅 26th September
⏰ 4:00pm – 6:00pm

🎃 FINAL Halloween Castings 🎃 

We’re on the look-out for the final performers to complete our teams for a series of Halloween events across the U.K. 

Contracts include:
😱 Adult Halloween Event (5pm - 11pm, 23rd Oct - 1st Nov) in Midlands 
👻 Family Halloween Event (11am - 4pm, 25th - 31st Oct) in Liverpool

💰Various competitive rates of pay dependent on contract.

If available and interested, please email Info@LaughingBulldogEvents.co.uk with a headshot of yourself and a brief cover letter. Thanks!

‼️ Casting Call ‼️

​

Für einen Werbespot suchen wir 2 männliche Darsteller 🎬

​

Rollen:

25–35 Jahre, vorzugsweise dunkle Haare, Muttersprache Deutsch

40–50 Jahre, vorzugsweise dunkle Haare, Muttersprache Deutsch

​

📅 Drehtermin: 22. oder 23.09.2025 (nur 1 Tag, aber bitte beide Tage verfügbar sein)

💶 Gage: 669 € pauschal pro Person

✈️ Reisekosten: werden komplett übernommen

📍 Drehort: Kopenhagen

​

👉 Kommentiere mit ❤️ und du erhältst den Bewerbungslink!

Nach deiner Anmeldung bekommst du automatisch eine Mail, in der wir weitere Infos von dir abfragen (bitte ggf. auch im Spam nachsehen!).

​

Bitte bewirb dich nur, wenn du an den genannten Tagen verfügbar bist.

​

Wir freuen uns auf euch!

Dein Castfinder-Team ✨

message.text:
Looking to cast for cruises, hotels, resorts, amusement parks, or festivals? Here’s the fastest way to run turnkey auditions with our agency. 👉Book your audition:
https://risingstars-talents.com/entertainment-casting-agency-turnkey-auditions/?utm_source=reg-FB-RS-rstM

✅HOW IT WORKS:
1. Send your brief: roles, show format, dates, budget, location(s) or remote.
2. Choose audition format: Online (Zoom/Teams), On-site, or Hybrid.
3. We prep everything: casting panel, schedule, tech host, brief pack.
4. Audition day: we host, time-stamp and record every take.
5. Shortlist in 24–72h: links, notes, availability, indicative rates.
6. Finalize & onboard: callbacks, offers, contracts, visas, travel & riders.

🏆Why us
27 years · 49,000+ talents · 47 countries · 27 managers
The Best Talents for The Best Shows.

#RisingStarsAgency #EntertainmentCasting #Auditions #TalentSourcing #CruiseEntertainment #HotelEntertainment #ResortEntertainment #ThemeParkEntertainment #FestivalEntertainment

‼️ Casting Call ‼️

​

Für einen Werbespot suchen wir 2 männliche Darsteller 🎬

​

Rollen:

25–35 Jahre, vorzugsweise dunkle Haare, Muttersprache Deutsch

40–50 Jahre, vorzugsweise dunkle Haare, Muttersprache Deutsch

​

📅 Drehtermin: 22. oder 23.09.2025 (nur 1 Tag, aber bitte beide Tage verfügbar sein)

💶 Gage: 669 € pauschal pro Person

✈️ Reisekosten: werden komplett übernommen

📍 Drehort: Kopenhagen

​

👉 Kommentiere mit ❤️ und du erhältst den Bewerbungslink!

Nach deiner Anmeldung bekommst du automatisch eine Mail, in der wir weitere Infos von dir abfragen (bitte ggf. auch im Spam nachsehen!).

​

Bitte bewirb dich nur, wenn du an den genannten Tagen verfügbar bist.

​

Wir freuen uns auf euch!

Dein Castfinder-Team ✨

Kogo: Fotografów / Modeli 
Kiedy i Gdzie: 5.10 Wrocław - Czasoprzestrzeń
Kto: Fundacja Fotospacery
Temat: Fotospacery - Powrót do Przeszłości 
Zapraszamy wszystkich chętnych do wzięcia udzialu w naszych cyklicznym wydarzeniu, a też kończącym ten sezon plenerowy. 
Zapraszamy zarówno osoby które dopiero zaczynają jak i bardziej doświadczone osoby do stworzenia tego cudownego wydarzenia razem z nami! 
Nie czekaj, zapisz sobie datę i powróć z nami do przeszłości! 

 Podczas naszych spotkań nabierzesz niezbędnego doświadczenia, lub pogłębisz swój warsztat! :)

WARSAW 24.09 Wednesday

For a feature series, I am looking for an ASIAN ACTOR or talented extra, man approx. 50 years old. 

A spoken role, at least communicative Polish language is necessary.

Rate: PLN 900 per shooting day.

Travel expenses covered, whitout accomodation.

Please attach a showreel in Polish as a YouTube link to your application.

APPLICATIONS:

Send to: ewelina.wika@podtytulem.pl

Email subject: ASIAN

In the content: full name, age, phone number, city

In the attachment:

– the most recent, good quality photo of the face (portrait, in daylight, without filters)

– full-body photo (color, without glasses, head coverings, or accompanying persons)

🌆 CAPE TOWN CBD CASTING CALL! 🎥
Street Party Vibes x Paid Shoot x Big Energy
Ready to show your talent? Step into the spotlight!
🎉 THE UZUAL SUSPECTS are throwing down in the streets of Cape Town CBD this FRIDAY & SATURDAY, and we’re casting MALE & FEMALE talent to be part of this epic street party production!
🕺 No experience? No problem.
🎬 Looking to start your acting journey? Let’s go!
🔥 Got the vibe, style, or confidence? We want YOU!
💸 THIS IS A PAID SHOOT
📍 Location: Cape Town CBD
📆 Dates: This Friday & Saturday
🎭 Production: The Uzual Suspects
🎉 Expect street-style fun, camera time, and a whole vibe!
📲 If you're definitely available and ready to roll, WhatsApp MOIRA for all the info:
👉 +27 68 499 9959
Don’t wait around — show up, show out, and let Cape Town see what you’re made of! 🎬🔥

sharedPost.text:
This afternoon we had the pleasure of entertaining a full house for Pettswood WI with our performance of Mr Macabre's Inn. 

The WI is a unique organisation shaped by its members. In 1915, it  set out to give women a voice and to be a force for good in the community. Today, it is the largest women’s organisation in the UK priding itself on being a trusted place for all women of all generations, to share experiences and learn from each other.

It's 1840, Victorian England… Deep in the heart of the Kent countryside, not far from the hop farm and the coastline is a secluded little hamlet, with a very old established Inn…
Has Mr. Macabre the Innkeeper being pulling more than pints?
What's the secret ingredient in Mrs. Macabre's popular pies?
Does Tomjon Jones poach more than eggs?

Watch the events unfold and see if you can solve the Murder at Macabre’s Inn?

Next week we are performing Mr Macabre's Inn on Friday for Sheppey 92.5FM and on Saturday in Boughton Monchelsea, Maidstone.
